<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.10.9">
<l>vāṉat teḻunta maḻaimukil pōleṅkum</l>
<l>kāṉattu mēyntu kaḷittu viḷaiyāṭi</l>
<l>ēṉat turuvā yiṭantavim maṇṇiṉai</l>
<l>tāṉattē vaittāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">taraṇi yiṭantāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like a rain cloud high in the sky,</l>
<l rend="indent">grazing through the forest everywhere,</l>
<l>Rejoicing in play, as a boar he dug up this earth</l>
<l>Because of him who put it [the earth] in place,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end.</l>
<l>Because of him who dug up the earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we’re at our end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
